{"type":"message","id":"2de7d1dc","parentId":"b67a5fa1","timestamp":"2026-03-11T05:33:23.727Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to read HEARTBEAT.md and follow its instructions. Let me go through the checklist:\n\n1. Read memory/NOW.md - to confirm current priority\n2. Check memory/backlog.md - for pending tasks\n3. Check delivery-queue/failed directory - for dead letters\n4. Check memory/job_errors.md - for unhandled task failure alerts\n5. Update memory/NOW.md\n\nThen I need to send a confirmation message to DingTalk following the format:\n- 🟢 心跳正常 | {time} | 无待办 (if everything is normal)\n- 🟡 心跳正常 | {time} | 待办: {brief description} (if there are pending items)\n- 🔴 心跳异常 | {time} | 异常: {problem description} (if there are issues)\n\nIf there are unhandled alerts in job_errors.md, I must include the alert summary.\n\nLet me read all the required files.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-8673ef0eb0b14da298442388e9d40566","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-93123deffdc14eae880cb811f55af563","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/NOW.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-64db503b2e194919ad4d14ca8c763f97","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/backlog.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-0c05cd735363498fb82fb3324f6da73b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /root/.openclaw/workspace/delivery-queue/failed/ 2>/dev/null || echo \"Directory empty or does not exist\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-e1135d1f59f54ac3bfc4ced13eb4f293","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/job_errors.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"