{"type":"message","id":"9a50eaae","parentId":"ac9d284f","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:00:28.502Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to execute a heartbeat check by reading HEARTBEAT.md and following its procedures. Let me read the required files and perform the checks.\n\nCurrent time is 10:59 PM (Asia/Shanghai), which is 22:59. According to HEARTBEAT.md, the scheduled heartbeat times are 09:00 and 21:00. This is after the 21:00 time but still within the same day.\n\nI need to:\n1. Read HEARTBEAT.md\n2. Read memory/NOW.md to confirm current priorities\n3. Check memory/backlog.md for pending tasks\n4. Check delivery-queue/failed directory for dead letters\n5. Check memory/job_errors.md for unhandled failure alerts\n6. Update memory/NOW.md with the heartbeat timestamp\n7. Send a confirmation message to DingTalk\n\nLet me proceed with the checks.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-55b501a92f9c49d3ac9c25e5a2ae5fc7","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-40bfb463d06b45d6b11687ffea243858","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/NOW.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-b44d9f9f3af34462a60937fdd1942cfa","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/backlog.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-89e9eba1b152435098c739d72b0b5d2c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /root/.openclaw/workspace/delivery-queue/failed/ 2>/dev/null || echo \"Directory empty or does not exist\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-28ab229185084b1d9a6bc3fa1d0e82db","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/job_errors.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"